data.name: lblFire.ToolTip
data.value: Fire Signs tend to be passionate, dynamic, and temperamental. They get angry quickly, but they also forgive easily. They are adventurers with immense energy. They are physically very strong and are a source of inspiration for others. Fire signs are intelligent, self-aware, creative, and idealistic people, always ready for action.

data.name: lblHealth.Text
data.value: This is a great week for recognition! Have you been a strong team player, a diligent worker, or an uncomplaining family member lately? This week, that recognition you've been trying to go without may float towards you, so take it in, and don't be self-effacing! In fact, you're probably not giving yourself enough credit. What is the most positive thing you could do for yourself this week? If it's getting a little exercise, that would be highly recommended.

data.name: lblLuck.Text
data.value: This week is great for you, and you will have plenty of energy. Today is a good day to start over; You have the opportunity to rethink many things and create a solid emotional base. Free yourself from doubts and negative feelings. Take advantage of this this week to test new terrains and launch yourself to conquer what you want.

data.name: lblTravel.Text
data.value: Give up your seat on the bus to someone at the beginning of the week -- or if you're traveling in style, find an equivalent good deed you can do wordlessly. Little interactions like this can brighten your trip and improve your karma simultaneously. And you may need good karma (and a good attitude) to deal with some minor or major disruptions that come your way on Wednesday or Thursday. Handle them with aplomb, and you'll be back to all sorts of exploring fun (and good luck) by the weekend.

data.name: lblMoney.Text
data.value: This week may present some interesting issues for you, who'd prefer to be spending money on the home and family. Tension means that beauty and comfort may need to take a temporary back seat so you can get a more conservative financial plan in place. Your closest confidants have your best interests at heart. Trust their instincts when it comes to saving and investing money. Together you can make great things happen.

data.name: lblCareer.Text
data.value: No one will take you seriously at your job today unless you have solid facts and concrete evidence to back up what you say. If you have to make any sort of presentation, be sure you are well prepared. Others will see through the holes in your plan.

data.name: lblLove.Text
data.value: Now's a good time to reconsider some of your ideas and beliefs concerning a current relationship. If you have been under the misguided apprehension that partnerships were all about angst, self-development, and the sharing of each other's less desirable qualities, then be prepared to be thrust into an orgy of laughter, carefree caresses, and good-humored enjoyment. Love can be fun too you know!
